New York Stock Exchange
U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission
Financial Industry Regulatory Authority







Daiwa Capital Markets America Inc. (DCMA) is a corporation organized under the laws of New York, a broker-dealer registered with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, a futures commission merchant (FCM) regulated as such by the CFTC, and a primary dealer in U.S. government securities. Copyright ownership of this homepage belongs to Daiwa Capital Markets America Inc. The use or duplication of any information on this website for unauthorized use is prohibited by copyright law. Daiwa Capital Markets America Inc. makes no guarantees regarding the content of this website, and accepts no responsibility for any errors in the content or any loss or damages based on the information contained on this site.




